1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:09,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我必須繼續工作賺錢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

2
00:00:09,120 --> 00:00:10,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不然我們就完了，克萊夫，完蛋了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

3
00:00:11,040 --> 00:00:15,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-貝兒，貝兒吉柏森</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-她要借助我的專業</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

4
00:00:15,480 --> 00:00:17,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當然了，她是我的競爭者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

5
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:23,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她的應用程式裝在人們的手腕上</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>像是在越南，摩洛哥和秘魯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

6
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:24,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但你在做什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

7
00:00:25,680 --> 00:00:27,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只是乾坐在這裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

8
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:29,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我和我的事業經常做慈善募款</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

9
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:33,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也許找時間讓男孩們約來家裡玩？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們可以聊聊一些可能性</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

10
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:34,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她會害死你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

11
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:38,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你選擇這條路，你會沒命</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

12
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:40,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你聽說過黑色藥膏嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

13
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:42,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不要噓我！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

14
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:45,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們對我下毒，你覺得沒關係嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

15
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>爸覺得我應該離開你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

16
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:48,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們懷疑你是不是真的有癌症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

17
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:51,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>克萊夫，他們為什麼會這樣懷疑？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

18
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:54,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不能破壞了我們母子的關係</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

19
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:56,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>又拿你爸媽的廢話來教訓我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

20
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:59,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽，媽？拜託誰來幫忙好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

21
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽媽！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

22
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒關係，沒事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

23
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:03,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-媽！</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-她只是摔了一跤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

24
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:04,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒事了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

25
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:10,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（以下劇情來自真實故事的啟發）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

26
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:14,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（某些角色與事件為創作與虛構）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

27
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:17,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（非常心痛）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

28
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:21,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>女人，尤其是成為母親後</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

29
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:26,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們必須有三頭六臂</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>滿足所有人的需要</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

30
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:29,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我幾乎是做牛做馬</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

31
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:32,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>給那個女孩想要的一切</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

32
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:35,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果她弄丟了她最心愛的泰迪熊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

33
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:38,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們相信</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們會大老遠跑去土文巴嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

34
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:40,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她的父親，也就是我丈夫安迪跟我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

35
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:44,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們一路開車回到土文巴</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

36
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:48,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>去同一間嬰兒用品店</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>買同樣一個泰迪熊娃娃</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

37
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們就是這麼愛她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

38
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-海克！</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-那是誰？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

39
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一個客戶，我沒邀請她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

40
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:59,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你看到了嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>她接受採訪，真是鬼話連篇！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

41
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:04,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她只是個傻女孩，老是好高騖遠</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

42
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:08,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>入不敷出，而且對電腦上癮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

43
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:12,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我告訴過她，那不是真實世界</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

44
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>並不健康</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

45
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:18,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你應該要保護我的！你想整死我嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

46
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:20,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-什麼？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我要打給《60分鐘》，聽到了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

47
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:23,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你別想拿到佣金了，別碰我！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

48
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-這是孩子的派對！</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-那是你的前妻嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

49
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:28,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我相信你應該知道</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>他需要就醫解決藥物濫用問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

50
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-回家吧，貝兒</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你才滾回家</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

51
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:34,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>希望你自己收拾好爛攤，好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

52
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:37,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>合作到此為止！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

53
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:40,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有佣金</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

54
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒問題，寶貝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

55
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>光與愛</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

56
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>送你光與愛</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

57
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:54,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我都不知道該怎麼說</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>那ㄚ頭的作為讓我們多沒面子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

58
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:58,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她欺騙了那麼多窮人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

59
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:01,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而我們在她的人生中</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>只扮演無足輕重的角色</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

60
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:05,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對此我由衷地感到抱歉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

61
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-很不錯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

62
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:11,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-都拍到了嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

63
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:16,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們接到飯店打來的電話</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

64
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:19,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是不是忘了拿什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

65
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:25,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們對小冰櫃和客房服務費有點疑問</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

66
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這樣啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

67
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:32,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是你說可以點晚餐和早餐的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

68
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:41,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-那是我們提供的衣褲套裝嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

69
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:45,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她會掛回架上嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

70
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有，好吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

71
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:52,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這不是真實故事</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>請詳閱完全免責聲明</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

72
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:56,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒吉柏森沒有因此收到半分酬勞</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

73
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我也沒有</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

74
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不是錢的問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

75
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:04,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有很多雜誌社的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

76
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:08,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>開出兩千美元的價碼，兩千美元</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

77
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:13,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我說：“你們可是</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>市值數十億美元的公司”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

78
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:18,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>無論多少代價</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我都不會出賣我女兒，謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

79
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:20,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這就是母愛</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

80
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:23,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>惹人厭，也令人讚佩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

81
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:26,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>吃力不討好，成就感滿滿</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

82
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>說到底…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

83
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我愛我的女兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

84
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就這麼簡單</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

85
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:36,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>《神效蘋果醋》</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

86
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:40,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（如果你捏造謊言或健康問題</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>來勾起外界的興趣）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

87
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:43,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（代表你有嚴重的人格缺陷）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

88
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:45,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（貝兒吉柏森</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>臉書貼文，2014年）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

89
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:53,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>看起來很真實，整整持續了40分鐘</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

90
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:06,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我一直在想克萊夫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

91
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他能從中得到什麼好處？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

92
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:12,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>錢，一袋又一袋的錢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

93
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你覺得是這樣嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

94
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有點難摸透他的心思</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

95
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:20,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>軟柿子？斯德哥爾摩症候群？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

96
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:23,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-他並不是清白無辜</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你覺得他會跟我談嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

97
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就算私下受訪，可能就足夠了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

98
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我看不會</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

99
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是說，他有點…我說不上來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

100
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>雖然你可以感覺到…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

101
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>該死的臭婊子！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

102
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>臭女人！狗娘養的！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

103
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>其實很難說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

104
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

105
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

106
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>起來，換衣服</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

107
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不舒服</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

108
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:58,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，所以我們要去醫院</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你要穿運動服還是牛仔褲？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

109
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，小蜜</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

110
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:27,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我剛剛聽說…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

111
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我真的不知道該說什麼…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

112
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:34,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我在這裡，你可以打給我</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>有需要就打給我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

113
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:36,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>請節哀順變</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

114
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我愛你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

115
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>香奈爾？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

116
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>克萊夫逼我去醫院</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

117
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:47,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我回來時你還會在嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們可以一起過夜</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

118
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>小蜜的媽媽剛過世</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

119
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:01,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>什麼時候的事？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

120
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不知道，我不…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

121
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:08,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們在去墨西哥的途中，然後…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

122
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不知…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

123
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:16,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我真的不清楚，所以…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你要去看她嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

124
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:19,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，她以前會開車送我去學校</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

125
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:23,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我一直在那裡生活，我在那裡長大的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

126
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:27,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你真的應該去一趟，別擔心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

127
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們可以透過電郵做準備工作</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

128
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可憐的蜜拉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

129
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

130
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:41,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真的，可憐的蜜拉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

131
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:47,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（安息吧，塔瑪拉布萊克）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

132
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:51,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（令人哀痛，你已經和天使同在了）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

133
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>走吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

134
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:15,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>等等，我要訂花給蜜…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

135
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你做什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

136
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:21,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你像個瘋子一樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

137
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:23,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你癲癇發作，得去看醫生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

138
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不要這樣好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

139
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:33,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那個小男孩嚇壞了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

140
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:35,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他在我懷裡顫抖</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

141
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:37,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很抱歉我昏倒了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

142
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:40,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-好</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你覺得我是壞媽媽</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

143
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-就像娜塔莉</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不，我覺得你需要就醫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

144
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>把手機還我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

145
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>克萊夫，給我…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

146
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>都是因為你父母</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

147
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>每次你回阿得雷德，他們就把你洗腦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

148
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你在我的腦海裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

149
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:08,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你他媽的一直在這裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

150
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒事，小傢伙，嘿</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

151
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒事了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

152
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:25,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你不進去，就到此為止</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

153
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不玩了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

154
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:40,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們有這麼美滿的家庭</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

155
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們的感情這麼緊密</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

156
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就像靈魂伴侶</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

157
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:49,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你離開，他會傷心欲絕</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

158
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很多孩子經常在不同家庭之間遊走</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

159
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們會適應的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

160
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:58,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>什麼意思？共享監護權嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

161
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你、我跟奈森？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

162
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那怎麼行得通？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

163
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:11,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他的出生證明上沒有你的名字</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

164
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你沒有任何權利</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

165
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這太不公平了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

166
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很抱歉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

167
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:28,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對不起，拜託</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

168
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:32,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我保證我會去看醫生，好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

169
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我去約時間</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

170
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:38,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你可以跟我一起去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

171
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:42,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好了，我們回家吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

172
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:45,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這樣小可愛才可以拆禮物，好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

173
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，不要別這樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

174
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>克萊夫，拜託</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

175
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我保證，我保證我會去，好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

176
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>拜託了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

177
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:01,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>上車</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

178
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>拜託</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

179
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>求你了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

180
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:11,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真他媽亂來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

181
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:13,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>永遠別再在他面前搞這齣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

182
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:45,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這份是原味</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

183
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:50,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我幫你選了糙米，而不是花椰菜米</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

184
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>比較有飽足感</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

185
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有人要喝東西嗎？要不要水？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

186
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不用</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

187
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:07,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>爸，我在想我們可以找</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>跟外婆一樣的葬儀社</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

188
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

189
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:15,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你還記得他們嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你喜歡他們的服務嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

190
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:25,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她死得很痛苦，對吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

191
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:32,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她死得很痛苦，對吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

192
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:38,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

193
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:52,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝，阿洛，但我要去睡覺了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

194
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:53,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

195
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:56,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也該離開了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

196
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>蜜拉，你要上床睡覺嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

197
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:24,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>等一下</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

198
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:26,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，小蜜</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

199
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:30,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你還在用那種黑色藥膏嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

200
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:35,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我看了很多相關資料</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>或許你應該把它扔掉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

201
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:40,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>小蜜？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

202
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>知道了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

203
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:19,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，你有看到茱莉辦公室的信嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

204
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:22,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們寄來新書發表會的賓客名單</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

205
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有點失望</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

206
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:27,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很多老傢伙</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你能多邀幾號有趣的人物嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

207
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

208
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:30,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你真的很有兩把刷子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

209
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:33,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>明明懷著諸多疑慮</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你為什麼繼續替她工作？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

210
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不知道</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

211
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:37,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的內臟都揪成一團了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

212
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我覺得好噁心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

213
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:41,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>時時刻刻都是如此</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

214
00:14:42,400 --> 00:14:44,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她開始讓我感到厭惡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

215
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>兩個佛陀碗？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

216
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:49,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真可口，你們家的香菇最好吃</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

217
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-是野外採的嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-是就好了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

218
00:14:51,280 --> 00:14:53,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那個女服務生</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>是不是用奇怪眼神看我們？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

219
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:56,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不知道，也許她覺得你會吃霸王餐</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

220
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:01,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你看</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-嗯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

221
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她是粉絲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

222
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我去打聲招呼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

223
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:23,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

224
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

225
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>情況怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

226
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:31,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

227
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:34,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我送了花過去，不知道你有沒有收到</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

228
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:36,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們要求捐款</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

229
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:38,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉，這樣說有點壞</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

230
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:41,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，沒關係，那個…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

231
00:15:42,760 --> 00:15:47,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我本來想過去一趟</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但阿洛說你可能不希望…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

232
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:51,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只有邀家人而已，所以…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們會再找時間舉辦告別式</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

233
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:56,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>喬還好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

234
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我得掛了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

235
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:03,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>等等，小蜜，我…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

236
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:09,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我覺得我有很多地方要道歉，但是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

237
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:16,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還有，我跟貝兒說了塔瑪拉的事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

238
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:19,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她就在他的IG上發文</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

239
00:16:19,680 --> 00:16:22,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這讓我很反感</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

240
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:23,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，我看到了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

241
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我當時在太平間</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

242
00:16:27,920 --> 00:16:29,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>機場有太平間</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

243
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:32,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-誰想得到？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對不起，小蜜</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

244
00:16:32,520 --> 00:16:35,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為什麼要道歉？貝兒真是體貼入微</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

245
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:38,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>從未見過我母親卻硬要裝熟來蹭熱度</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

246
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:41,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她好親切，她得乳癌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

247
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:44,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我邀她來參加新書發表會</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你登記一下</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

248
00:16:45,520 --> 00:16:46,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

249
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:49,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>小蜜？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

250
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我就不打擾你了，好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

251
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就這樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

252
00:16:58,520 --> 00:17:01,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>臨界點，被打臉</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>隨便你怎麼說，總之我受夠了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

253
00:17:01,760 --> 00:17:05,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（面對自戀者，如何安排介入手段）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

254
00:17:10,600 --> 00:17:13,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>預計到達時間前五分鐘</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我傳簡訊給她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

255
00:17:13,320 --> 00:17:15,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（我會過去，我們需要談一談）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

256
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:18,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你到底有沒有</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

257
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:22,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他媽的腦癌？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

258
00:17:23,360 --> 00:17:24,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（我到了，在大門口）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

259
00:17:24,840 --> 00:17:26,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我中途因為緊張停下來拉屎</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

260
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:29,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的靜止心率每分鐘高達99次</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

261
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:31,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>順便說一聲，已經接近心搏過速了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

262
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:37,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗨，好高興你來了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

263
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:40,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真有趣，好了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我有個驚喜要給你，快進來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

264
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:43,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

265
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:53,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>雖然不是一模一樣，但很接近了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

266
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你喜歡嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

267
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:58,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，嗯…好吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

268
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:01,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們能不能…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

269
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:05,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可以請你坐下嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

270
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:07,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是致敬，不是模仿</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

271
00:18:08,760 --> 00:18:09,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

272
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:13,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

273
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:15,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>香奈爾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

274
00:18:19,680 --> 00:18:21,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們墜入愛河了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

275
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

276
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:27,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我今晚來這裡…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

277
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:30,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是想問你…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

278
00:18:32,600 --> 00:18:34,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你有腦癌嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

279
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她怎麼反應？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

280
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:38,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>哭得淅瀝嘩啦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

281
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:47,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>“你為什麼要這樣？”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

282
00:18:47,600 --> 00:18:50,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>“為什麼對我這麼惡劣？”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

283
00:18:52,360 --> 00:18:53,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

284
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:58,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你為什麼這麼做？我不明白</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-這是你的核心圈子，好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

285
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:02,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你在這裡很安全</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>事情從這裡開始，也要在這裡結束</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

286
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:06,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我以為蜜拉才是你的核心圈子</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對，蜜拉也是我朋友</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

287
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:09,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-但你可以有很多核心…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我聽說她癌症復發</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

288
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:14,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>並沒有，沒這回事</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你從哪裡聽來的？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

289
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:18,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們鬧翻了嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>如果是因為我，我很過意不去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

290
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:20,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-她的粉絲人數…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-蜜拉沒那麼缺乏自信</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

291
00:19:20,800 --> 00:19:22,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你說她是你見過最好勝的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

292
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:25,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>記得我們在那家巷道酒吧</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>喝莫西多調酒的時候嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

293
00:19:26,040 --> 00:19:28,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你說她10年級時有飲食障礙症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

294
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:30,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>差點要住院治療</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>只因為她想成為最瘦的女生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

295
00:19:30,560 --> 00:19:32,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你有沒有腦癌？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

296
00:19:32,800 --> 00:19:35,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>給我看任何一樣醫療證據</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

297
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:38,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一張掃描片</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>或腫瘤科醫生的手寫病歷都好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

298
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:40,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我以後再也不會提這件事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

299
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:43,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我全丟了，我不要家裡有那種能量</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

300
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:45,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-誰診斷的？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你為什麼攻擊我？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

301
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:47,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只是癲癇發作，結果人人都討厭我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

302
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:50,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>哪一位醫生，貝兒？打電話過去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

303
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:51,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你見過菲爾醫生了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

304
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:54,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>見鬼，你有沒有搞錯？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

305
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:56,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>菲爾醫生打赤腳耶</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

306
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:59,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>小聲一點，克萊夫和小傢伙在睡覺</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

307
00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:01,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你說得對，叫他過來，克萊夫？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

308
00:20:03,360 --> 00:20:04,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，克萊夫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

309
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:08,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們得談談貝兒的事，克萊夫？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

310
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:11,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你躲在浴室裡嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

311
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:15,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉，失陪一下，喂？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

312
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:17,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>茱兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

313
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:19,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>茱兒，是我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

314
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:21,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>出事了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

315
00:20:21,280 --> 00:20:23,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不知道你有沒有</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>跟任何人談過，但…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

316
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:25,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝拉，親愛的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

317
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:27,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>冷靜下來，怎麼回事？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

318
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:28,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>克萊夫，拜託</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

319
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:32,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>克萊夫，我需要你在場</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

320
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:35,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你有聽說我的癌症傳言嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-什麼傳言？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

321
00:20:35,520 --> 00:20:38,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>外面有一些流言蜚語，但都不是事實</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

322
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:40,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>要是你聽到風聲</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>請理解那是一個眼紅的朋友…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

323
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:43,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>喂，你跟講電話？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

324
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:45,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-那是誰？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我要掛了，愛你，再見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

325
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:50,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-剛剛是誰？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-一個朋友</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

326
00:20:50,840 --> 00:20:52,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧，克萊夫，不好意思</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

327
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:56,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-可以請你過來客廳嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-能不能讓我喝點水？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

328
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:58,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不行，麻煩立刻過來客廳</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

329
00:20:58,720 --> 00:21:00,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒，你也是，快過來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

330
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:03,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，是這樣的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

331
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:05,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>聽著，我不是為人父母</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

332
00:21:06,040 --> 00:21:08,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我真的認為你兒子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

333
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:12,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有權知道他媽媽並沒有快要死了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>簡單來說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

334
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:15,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而且克萊夫認同我的看法</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>對吧，克萊夫？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

335
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:17,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-對，是的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

336
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:21,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-大體上認同</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-所以我們要一起去醫院</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

337
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:23,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我癲癇發作後，我們已經去過了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-這個嘛…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

338
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:24,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>然後我決定…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

339
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:28,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-克萊夫，你遲疑了是什麼意思？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我們去過醫院了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

340
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:32,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們認為我沒時間</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>再另外找一個醫療團隊診治</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

341
00:21:32,280 --> 00:21:35,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只想好好享受能跟家人共處的時光</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

342
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:38,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不該被強迫證實或否認</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

343
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:41,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就像狗仔隊在琳賽蘿涵剛剛流產時</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

344
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:43,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>到處追著她跑</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

345
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:47,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>懷孕是她的私事，跟任何人無關</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

346
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:49,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>知道嗎，寶貝，我…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

347
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>實際上我完全認同你說的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

348
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:56,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你是很棒的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

349
00:21:56,920 --> 00:22:01,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真的，我知道你的心胸多寬大</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>要是我不相信你，那…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

350
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:03,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我就不會在這裡了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

351
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:06,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我老早就去找媒體爆料</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

352
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:13,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那個…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

353
00:22:15,840 --> 00:22:19,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我需要薄荷茶和一些零食</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

354
00:22:20,560 --> 00:22:21,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可以麻煩你嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

