00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:28,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>得腦癌，你不需要知道這些</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>知道了對你有什麼用處？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

587
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:30,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這種行為真令人反感</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我都說不能問了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

588
00:38:33,960 --> 00:38:37,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-這些事不重要也不有趣</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-他們可能還是會問</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

589
00:38:37,680 --> 00:38:41,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那只是我另一部分私生活的枝微末節</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

590
00:38:41,080 --> 00:38:45,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很樂意轉移話題，像是說…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

591
00:38:46,480 --> 00:38:49,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>“抱歉，這跟我的現況毫不相關”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

592
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:52,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>四兩撥千金就好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

593
00:38:53,120 --> 00:38:55,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>話語權在我們手上，不是他們</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

594
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:04,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗯，我只是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

595
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:08,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>覺得這恐怕滿足不了那些小報記者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

596
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:11,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但是…讓我們繼續吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

597
00:39:12,640 --> 00:39:16,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我實在不想那麼難搞</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

598
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:19,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但這是普拿疼，不是諾洛芬</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

599
00:39:23,600 --> 00:39:24,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>茱莉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

600
00:39:26,200 --> 00:39:29,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒想走了，她說偏頭痛越來越嚴重</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

601
00:39:30,240 --> 00:39:31,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

602
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:58,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（你離目標很近了！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

603
00:39:59,560 --> 00:40:06,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（我們快達標了，費歐娜！</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>很快會有更多！親親，貝兒留）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

604
00:40:26,960 --> 00:40:28,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你在腫塊上塗抹什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

605
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:31,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>黑色藥膏</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

606
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:42,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這裡，這裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

607
00:40:42,600 --> 00:40:44,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還有這裡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

608
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:49,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>五年前長在你右前臂的惡性肉瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

609
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:51,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>已經透過淋巴結轉移了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

610
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:55,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在你的右肺、肋骨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

611
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>薦骨…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

612
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>和左股骨都有癌細胞</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

613
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:04,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧，所以現在該怎麼辦？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

614
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:06,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是要…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

615
00:41:07,200 --> 00:41:09,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>做放療或化療嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

616
00:41:09,720 --> 00:41:12,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>都聽你的，我們要不要…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

617
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:16,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有試驗性治療或免疫療法嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

618
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:19,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很可惜，蜜拉已經不符合</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>試驗性治療的資格了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

619
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:23,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

620
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:25,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她曾經有過機會</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

621
00:41:25,480 --> 00:41:27,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但已經失去了，我很遺憾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

622
00:41:30,040 --> 00:41:33,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>什麼意思？她不配接受試驗嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

623
00:41:33,520 --> 00:41:35,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她才28歲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

624
00:41:35,560 --> 00:41:37,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>病情太嚴重了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

625
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:44,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我會幫你們轉介一位</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>優秀的安寧照護專家</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

626
00:41:44,520 --> 00:41:45,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>以及輔導員</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

627
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:48,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當然你還沒走到那一步，但…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

628
00:41:49,080 --> 00:41:51,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>先做準備也許能比較放心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

629
00:41:55,680 --> 00:41:57,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我還有多久才到那個階段？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

630
00:41:58,160 --> 00:42:01,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我估計不到三個月</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

631
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:02,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>去你的三個月</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

632
00:42:03,520 --> 00:42:06,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我女兒來找你求助，你就要幫助她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

633
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:12,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們醫生坐在那裡</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>一副像上帝的樣子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

634
00:42:12,240 --> 00:42:15,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-那就拿出本事，創造奇蹟</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-爸，他做不到</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

635
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:17,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是什麼意思，你說啊？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

636
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:21,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為她當初沒聽你的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>所以現在要懲罰她嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

637
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:23,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>喬</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

638
00:42:24,200 --> 00:42:25,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是醫學</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

639
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:28,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不摻入個人偏見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

640
00:42:29,160 --> 00:42:33,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你女兒的癌症擴散了，我很遺憾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

641
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:35,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但疾病正在吞噬她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

642
00:42:38,480 --> 00:42:40,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對不起</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

643
00:42:42,640 --> 00:42:44,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>求你救救她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

644
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:48,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-拜託了，救救她，求求你</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-爸</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

645
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:52,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

646
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:56,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-他媽的想想辦法啊</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-他盡力了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

647
00:42:59,240 --> 00:43:00,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒關係</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

648
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:03,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-沒事的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對不起，很抱歉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

649
00:43:05,440 --> 00:43:06,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們走</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

650
00:43:32,320 --> 00:43:35,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那麼，把時間快轉到墨爾本</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

651
00:43:35,560 --> 00:43:37,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你當時心臟病發</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

652
00:43:38,040 --> 00:43:41,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還診斷出癌症，是在哪一家醫院？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

653
00:43:44,320 --> 00:43:46,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-彼得麥卡倫治癌中心</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-嗯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

654
00:43:46,320 --> 00:43:50,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你覺得你的腫瘤科醫生會不會樂意</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

655
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:53,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>出現在報導上或跟我們開記者會呢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

656
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:56,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>應該不會，因為我離開他的治療計畫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

657
00:43:56,760 --> 00:43:58,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他很不高興</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

658
00:43:58,840 --> 00:44:00,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那些醫生很在乎地盤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

659
00:44:03,000 --> 00:44:06,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這不要緊，我們可以…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

660
00:44:06,080 --> 00:44:08,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們可以用紙本病歷就好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

661
00:44:09,640 --> 00:44:11,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你手邊有嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-當然有</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

662
00:44:12,840 --> 00:44:16,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有些放在我媽家</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>可能需要花點時間翻找</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

663
00:44:18,320 --> 00:44:19,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她有點囤積傾向</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

664
00:44:33,800 --> 00:44:36,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一定會很成功，我保證</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

665
00:44:43,160 --> 00:44:46,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>預購的業績很出色，眾所期待呢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

666
00:44:46,960 --> 00:44:50,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝，傑瑞米，圍巾很好看</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

667
00:44:52,120 --> 00:44:54,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你今天好美，我們要等克萊夫嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

668
00:44:54,920 --> 00:44:57,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不用，他在橄欖球場</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

669
00:44:57,600 --> 00:45:00,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你知道的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>男生喜歡橄欖球，這樣比較好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

670
00:45:00,480 --> 00:45:03,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他有社恐，我兒子也很愛玩橄欖球</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

671
00:45:03,920 --> 00:45:06,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-等我一下</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-好，我們在前面碰頭</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

672
00:45:08,600 --> 00:45:09,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

673
00:45:11,560 --> 00:45:14,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我跟你保證</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我發誓我要求過他們拿掉我的名字</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

674
00:45:14,600 --> 00:45:16,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但他們不肯讓我解約</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

675
00:45:17,200 --> 00:45:18,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，聽著</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

676
00:45:18,720 --> 00:45:20,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>別擔心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

677
00:45:20,920 --> 00:45:23,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只是來看你撒謊的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

678
00:45:23,160 --> 00:45:24,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對著滿屋子的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

679
00:45:25,440 --> 00:45:28,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當然也是為了那些開胃小點</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>超美味的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

680
00:45:29,680 --> 00:45:32,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，哈囉，大家好啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

681
00:45:32,320 --> 00:45:36,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>哈囉，歡迎各位，讓發表會開始吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

682
00:45:37,320 --> 00:45:39,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>看到大家來到現場真的很開心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

683
00:45:40,240 --> 00:45:41,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

684
00:45:41,600 --> 00:45:44,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不認識我的來賓，我叫茱莉吉布斯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

685
00:45:47,760 --> 00:45:51,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是企鵝出版社</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>紙上生活風格藍燈部門的總監</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

686
00:45:52,240 --> 00:45:57,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在我想歡迎一位年輕女性上台</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

687
00:45:57,160 --> 00:45:58,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她是一個媽媽</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

688
00:45:59,240 --> 00:46:01,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是癌症倖存者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

689
00:46:01,880 --> 00:46:04,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也是創業家</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

690
00:46:04,720 --> 00:46:06,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在還多了一個作家的身分</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

691
00:46:07,240 --> 00:46:08,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒吉柏森</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

692
00:46:25,400 --> 00:46:27,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝，非常感謝大家</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

693
00:46:27,720 --> 00:46:28,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>天啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

694
00:46:29,840 --> 00:46:31,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真的好榮幸</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

695
00:46:32,240 --> 00:46:35,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真不敢相信我站在你們所有人面前</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

696
00:46:38,360 --> 00:46:41,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想要感謝我的媽媽</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

697
00:46:43,800 --> 00:46:45,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還有我的伴侶克萊夫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

698
00:46:47,080 --> 00:46:48,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還有我可愛的兒子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

699
00:46:50,400 --> 00:46:52,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當然，還有我的死黨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

700
00:46:53,760 --> 00:46:55,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你總是在背後支持我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

701
00:46:55,280 --> 00:46:56,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你有腦癌嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

702
00:46:57,200 --> 00:46:59,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒有把一切視為理所當然</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

703
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:02,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我也要藉這個機會</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

704
00:47:03,160 --> 00:47:05,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>向我的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

